@Rich_L1984 @kierisi @tejfbanalytics You can construct pieces outside the main ui function and add them in. I usually define each tabItem (for shinydashboard apps) in a separate file so I just need:

ui &lt;- dashboardPage(
  dashboardHeader(),
  dashboardSidebar(),
  dashboardBody(
    tabItems(tab1, tab2, tab3)
  )
)

